parameters: \n< Serena >There's no way I'm going back!
\n< Serena >Haa haa... I did it! It's the exit!!

\n< Serena >Haa, haa... I need to escape faster, much
faster...!

\n< Thug >Hey, over here! This flesh toilet got tired in a
place like this.
\n< Serena >Ahh, ah... D-Don't come... Don't get closer...!

\n< Thug >This damn brat! Making me go through all this
trouble!!

\n< Thug >Geez, you really think you can escape... I'm going
to thoroughly beat into you the reality of your
position so that you'll never have the desire to
run away again...!

\n< Serena >No! Nooo! I don't want to go there anymore! I want
to go back homeee!
\n< Serena >Haa, haa... If I've come this far...

After that, while my consciousness was hazy, I
somehow managed to escape to a safe place...
